normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />東京啫，唔好咁夜行靜嘅地方就無事<br />\n返大陸就唔好自己一個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a654828fc3bcdeeda622cf560383c4c0ed479672","tid":312313,"uid":98180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"24歲自己一個去大阪玩左10日，住hostel識左好q多人&hellip;一堆日本學生妹，4至5個台灣人，2個澳洲同1個法國。最好玩嘅旅行一定係自己一個去"},{"pid":"7537769b3c2a462191c5f8d2d653c6e33eaf495e","tid":312313,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9382950ba3fdf670b60e43f306242ac65cb5d7c3","tid":312313,"uid":47621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:13:07.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴絲分享<br />\n因為我個人喺香港都鳩鳩吓咁所以驚出到去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續努力上網做吓功課先"},{"pid":"5203bc0892675d645e4710d4b2e386403764c6d4","tid":312313,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"310c45134aaa9d483fab1e67c792994f67b1f78d","tid":312313,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"第一次去台灣先"},{"pid":"63a859be1ccbc4f51b21350f09949b97e166b989","tid":312313,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝各位巴絲分享<br />\n因為我個人喺香港都鳩鳩吓咁所以驚出到去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續努力上網做吓功課先</blockquote><br />\n識睇地圖 智商正常都無乜問題"},{"pid":"d7a10464ccb8e8c9894045fc75ed3c6f39b2ecb6","tid":312313,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7432fa0f99014625369a4469a78516801209d89","tid":312313,"uid":47621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝各位巴絲分享<br />\n因為我個人喺香港都鳩鳩吓咁所以驚出到去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續努力上網做吓功課先</blockquote><br />\n樓主諗住去邊<br />\n<br />\n我未去過旅行又唔想約朋友<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">無朋友</span></span> 所以想自己一個去但又唔知去邊好</blockquote><br />\n東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未去過旅行唔想約朋友+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a3fa52e93162f6d4f7a3344a7eb549210f7916","tid":312313,"uid":47621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去台灣先</blockquote><br />\n朋友都係咁建議 話近近哋又溝通到<br />\n但我又冇咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df79717359cb772fa67ebe979c1fa12431039ec","tid":312313,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"週經"},{"pid":"9c788c08801a4c5b8e5ce35d5380371ae70e2c47","tid":312313,"uid":28739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"一個人去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1fdb6d28033462b4b72f86dd37228f03bcd144","tid":312313,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"來緊8月自己去大馬，沒驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff9f39cd5ce14675d2df537f085ffa805d73fa5","tid":312313,"uid":123276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"我第一次旅行自己去 又係去東京 plan好曬路線呀 行程呀 就無咩問題 唔識就睇google map<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日本人同有啲旅客都好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己去到搭車唔係好熟 有人見到我懵下懵下咁 都主動黎問我有無野要幫手 我唔識日文又路癡都無穿無爛返到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff0507263d6900a1528fb900c2aa118f8716984","tid":312313,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"自己一個去過歐洲 之後就係東京 再之後又歐洲<br />\